$(document).ready(function(){$('#converter-overview').on('click','.tabs li a',function(){$(this).closest('.tabs').find('li.active').removeClass('active');$(this).parent().addClass('active');var tmpl=$(this).attr('data-tmpl');$('#converter-overview .right .tmpl').removeClass('active');$('#'+tmpl).addClass('active')});$('#converter-overview form').submit(function(event){event.preventDefault()});$('#toeDegrees, #toeMinutes, #toeRimDiameter').change(function(){convertToe()});$('#toeConvert.button').click(function(){convertToe()});$('#torqueNm').change(function(){convertTorque()});$('#torqueNmConvert.button').click(function(){convertTorque()});$('#pressureBar').change(function(){convertPressure()});$('#pressureBarConvert.button').click(function(){convertPressure()});$('#volumeLitres').change(function(){convertVolume()});$('#volumeLitresConvert.button').click(function(){convertVolume()});$('#lengthMm').change(function(){convertLength()});$('#lengthMmConvert.button').click(function(){convertLength()});$('#speedKmh').change(function(){convertSpeed()});$('#speedKmhConvert.button').click(function(){convertSpeed()})});function inchToMm(inches){return inches*25.4}function convertToe(){var degrees='';var minutes='';var diameter='';degrees=$('#toeDegrees').val().replace(/,/,'.');minutes=$('#toeMinutes').val().replace(/,/,'.');diameter=$('#toeRimDiameter').val().replace(/,/,'.');var result=inchToMm(diameter)*Math.sin((Number(degrees)+Number(minutes)/60)*Math.PI/180);$('#resultToe span').html(result.toFixed(3))}function convertTorque(){var torque='';torque=$('#torqueNm').val().replace(/,/,'.');var result=torque*0.7376;$('#resultTorque span').html(result.toFixed(2))}function convertPressure(){var pressure='';pressure=$('#pressureBar').val().replace(/,/,'.');var result=pressure*14.5038;$('#resultPressure span').html(result.toFixed(2))}function convertVolume(){var volume='';volume=$('#volumeLitres').val().replace(/,/,'.');var result=volume*1.7606;$('#resultVolume span').html(result.toFixed(2))}function convertLength(){var length='';length=$('#lengthMm').val().replace(/,/,'.');var result=length*0.0394;$('#resultMm span').html(result.toFixed(2))}function convertSpeed(){var speed='';speed=$('#speedKmh').val().replace(/,/,'.');var result=speed*0.6214;$('#resultSpeed span').html(result.toFixed(2))}